<subSubSection id="C32ADAB5FFF80F5CFAF0FA96C993FACF" pageId="10" pageNumber="193" type="activity">
<paragraph id="8B8F893EFFF80F5CFAF0FA96C993FACF" blockId="10.[1376,2582,1045,1626]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">
<emphasis id="B944552CFFF80F5CFAF0FA96CA3FFAE5" bold="true" box="[1376,1610,1321,1350]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Barbour’s Pygmy Rock Mouseis nocturnal andspecialized for climbing rocks.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
