<subSubSection id="C32ADAB5FFF80F5CFAF1FA20CA49F9A9" pageId="10" pageNumber="193" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8B8F893EFFF80F5CFAF1FA20CA49F9A9" blockId="10.[1376,2582,1045,1626]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">
<emphasis id="B944552CFFF80F5CFAF1FA20CACAFA1F" bold="true" box="[1377,1727,1439,1468]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Barbour’s Pygmy Rock Mouse occupies rocky habitat that is unlikely to becomethreatened in the near future.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
